OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FScotland and Northern Ireland
OL,6,Flook largely dry with plenty of
OL,7,Fsunshine. Meanwhile, England and Wales
OL,8,Fwill be rather cloudy with some rain,
OL,9,Fthis chiefly across northern and
OL,10,Fwestern England and Wales this
OL,11,Fmorning, then across southeast England
OL,12,Flater. Generally cooler.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA dry, though increasingly
OL,15,Fbreezy night in the north with clear
OL,16,Fspells allowing some frost to form.
OL,17,FCloudier and milder across England and
OL,18,FWales with patchy rain and some fog.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
