OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FMostly dry in the north on
OL,6,FSaturday with some sunshine. Turning
OL,7,Fwet in the far northwest, and
OL,8,Fgenerally breezy. Cloudier across
OL,9,FEngland and Wales with patchy rain,
OL,10,Fand early fog.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
